SIMPLE: unsorted
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsorted
<hw>Un*sort"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
sorted; not classified; <as>as, a lot of <ex>unsorted</ex>
goods</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not well selected; ill-chosen.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The purpose you undertake is dangerous; the friends you named
uncertain; the time itself <qex>unsorted</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsoul</ent>⟦br⟧
